name: Michigan vs Michigan State
summary: On October 26, 2024, the highly anticipated Michigan vs. Michigan State football rivalry will take place. The game will be televised nationally and fans can also watch it via live stream. The Paul Bunyan Trophy will be at stake, and both teams will be looking to add another chapter to their storied rivalry. According to experts, Michigan is favored to win, but Michigan State has a history of upsetting their rivals. The game is expected to be close, and the outcome could hinge on key plays and performances from both teams' quarterbacks. The atmosphere in Ann Arbor is sure to be electric as fans from both schools descend on the city for one of the biggest sporting events of the year.
